Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.28,0:02:55.28,screen,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\bord1\fs110\fsp15\fnFOT-Lyra Std DB\c&H020103&\3c&H00013A&\pos(960,700)}覺醒
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.01,0:24:56.02,screen,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\bord1\fs115\fsp15\fnFOT-Lyra Std DB\c&H020103&\3c&H00013A&\pos(960,700)}邁向更高的意志
